  31 Dec 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild,
  echoe-4.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Remove gemcutter dependency from gemspec: it is optional and not important
  for Gentoo itself.

  25 Oct 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #322175).

  29 Aug 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild:
  ia64 stable wrt #330327

  12 Aug 2010; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #330327

  01 Aug 2010; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #330327

*echoe-4.3.1-r1 (01 Aug 2010)

  01 Aug 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild,
  +echoe-4.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Move non-ruby18 support to a new revision to mark 4.3.1 stable.

  22 May 2010; Alex Legler <a3li@gentoo.org> echoe-4.3.1.ebuild:
  Add REE18 support

